                           =========================
                               Bus stats counter
                           =========================

Abstract:
~~~~~~~~
This unit was designed for statistics purpose. Using it we can simply investigate
which unit on bus (FrameLink or Internal bus) is not ready for sending/receiving
enough.


Author:
~~~~~~
Jan Stourac <xstour03@stud.fit.vutbr.cz>


